name: NEFilterManagerError
desc: Error codes specific to filter managers.

items.name: case configurationInvalid
items.desc: An error code that indicates the filter configuration is invalid.

items.name: case configurationDisabled
items.desc: An error code that indicates the filter configuration isn’t enabled.

items.name: case configurationStale
items.desc: An error code that indicates another process modfied the filter configuration since the last time the app loaded the configuration.

items.name: case configurationCannotBeRemoved
items.desc: An error code that indicates removing the configuration isn’t allowed.

items.name: case configurationPermissionDenied
items.desc: An error code that indicates the configuration lacks permission.

items.name: case configurationInternalError
items.desc: An error code that indicates an internal configuration error occurred.
